bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Connection Reestablished. Incoming Transmission from Pulsar>

Good.

I'm glad you're capable of the immense feat of pushing buttons.

What? You wanna medal or something?

Anyway, to more pressing matters.


An unknown alien force has invaded Meridia. Wiped out the United Stellar Nations fleet. Boom! Just like that.

They teleported many of their soldiers aboard this ship, and were busy scrambling my logic cores and searching for any reference to a \"Naaro Kora'thun\" in my databases.


I've detected large scale excavations on the surface of Meridia. The aliens are searching for something. I'm going to send you down to find out what.

But first, go collect some ammo and recharge your shields. You're going to need it.
There's an weapons cache downstairs, underneath the bridge. 
Hopefully, the aliens haven't completely ransacked it.


Then, return to this terminal and I'll teleport you down to Meridia.







<Page 1 of 2, press Right Arrow to view page 2> "
