bbcode_enabled = true
text = "And, if you try pull the \"Why don't we contact Earth??????????\" card, let me tell you this.



We are 2000 light years away from Earth.

Even at light speed, any infomation will not get there fast enough.

We're on our own out here, so it's best you cooperate with me.


Otherwise, I'm sure our new alien 'friends' would like to meet you for a 'friendly chat'.



So stop whining and go kill aliens for me.

<End Transmission. Message Transmitter - Pulsar, Message Reciever - Bridge Terminal>
















<Page 2 of 2. Press 'E' to exit Terminal, or press Left Arrow to view page 1>
"
